It seems a node's drawables are being left in the scene, if the node survives being removed from a scene (ie. is referenced somewhere else)

In 04_StaticScene, add this after line 114: https://github.com/urho3d/Urho3D/blob/master/Source/Samples/04_StaticScene/StaticScene.cpp#L114

```
    // keep node alive, after removing node from scene
    mushroomNode->AddRef();

    // Removing components does get rid of drawables in scene, once node is removed
    //mushroomNode->RemoveAllComponents();

    // if node is still alive, drawables are still in scene
    scene_->RemoveChild(mushroomNode);
```
